
menuconfig DRV_SPI_FLASH
    bool "spi_flash ['spi,flash']"
    default n
    help
        Example of adding device to board.dts:

        &lpspi3 {
            spi_flash@0{
                compatible = "spi,flash";
                label = "spiflash";
                reg = <0>; /* cs index, chipselects from the spi host */
                status = "disabled";
            };
        };
